headline: Top Technology and Security Executives Recognized at the 2025 SoCal ORBIE Awards
summary: LOS ANGELES, Oct. 24, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The 2025 SoCal ORBIE Awards recognized the exceptional leadership and innovation of top technology executives from Monster Beverage Corp, Epson America, AMN Healthcare Services, Emanate Health, LA Clippers and Intuit Dome, UCLA Anderson School of Management, Skyworks Solutions, Inc., and Sharp HealthCare.
